{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act23side_level_act23side_st02","storyGroup":"act23side","storySort":10,"storyDependence":"act23side_level_act23side_04_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"WB-ST-2","storyName":"信我所信","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act23side/level_act23side_st02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act23side_st02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":8,"next":10,"characters":["重岳","仇白","截云","左乐","槐天裴","老鲤","槐琥","林雨霞","杜遥夜","孟铁衣"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$storyendjp_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_storyendjp_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":4,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":5},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/82/Avg_bg_35_g11_yumendesert.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":6},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我生在江边。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":7},{"type":"subtitle","text":"爹跟我说，江水连通了整片大地，有一条够坚固的船，就能去任何地方。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":8},{"type":"subtitle","text":"爹最讨厌下雪，大雪封门，没有“生意”可做，全家都得饿肚子。我的名字就是这样来的。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":9},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我不晓得“生意”是什么，只是每个月底都见爹提着刀和物资回来，还有专门带给我的礼物。这时娘便一声不吭地分拣东西，帮爹浆洗沾血的袍子。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":10},{"type":"subtitle","text":"直到有一天，一群穿着铠甲的人，攻破了寨子。爹一辈子都活在江上，最终也葬身江底。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":11},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我只记住了为首的那个人。明明是大获全胜，但他看起来并没有多少欣喜，只是望着被血染红的江水出神。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"subtitle","text":"当时我只剩下一个念头。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":13},{"type":"subtitle","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":15},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我要报仇。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":16},{"type":"subtitle","id":17},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我打听到了那人的所在，也离开了家。从炎国的最东头，一直追到最西边。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":19},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我才知道，原来大地上不止有江，还有数不尽的山川和原野。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":20},{"type":"subtitle","text":"大地上的人们，有千万种活法，也有千万般辛苦。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":21},{"type":"subtitle","text":"水寨太小了，如果爹能出来看看，或许不会选择半辈子都做那样的营生。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":22},{"type":"subtitle","text":"爹说的不对。一艘船，能去的地方不多。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":23},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我终于来到了玉门。那人就站在城头上，脸上是和那时一模一样的神情，我多少能看懂了些。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":24},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我应该报仇。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":25},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":26},{"type":"subtitle","id":27},{"type":"dialog","id":28},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"charslot","id":30},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#1$1","id":31},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1","id":32},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/13/Avg_bg_35_g3_yumenobservationtower_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":33},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":34},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":35},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"......","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"事情就是这样。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"剑在槐武痴手里，以他的武功，左乐估计拿他没办法。","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"为这一个约定，他竟然在城里等了三年......倒是个有趣的人。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"太合的伤势怎样了？","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"还没醒。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"重伤太合先生的和前天刺杀魏彦吾的是同一人。她趁乱逃走，我不是对手，没能追上。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"现在左乐封了铸剑坊，不少武人都被......控制了起来。","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"天灾当前，现在守军和江湖人士又彻底撕破脸，玉门的局势只怕会更乱。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"也不能怪他冲动。","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"......这件事，你自己不出手，解决不了。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"左将军让我留守军营，我明目张胆跟他作对算怎么回事。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#11$1","focus":"l","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"你知道我说的不只是这几天的事。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"你马上就要离开，临行前总要给城里的那些仰慕着你的人一个交代。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"还是你觉得，解释不清的事，回避就够了？","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"......","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"大家都当你是我的学生，有时候连我自己都忘了你的来历，也将你当作录武官、左乐一辈的孩子。","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"可我从没叫过你一声“老师”。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"我也的确不能算是。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"你的悟性很高，剑术多半是靠自己琢磨，我能教你的，本来就有限。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"毕竟是你对所有人隐瞒了我的身份，让我能留在玉门。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"总不能看着一个孩子再流落荒野......","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"你从来不担心我会动手杀你？还是认定我永远都赢不了你？","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"要想报仇，又何必要在武功上胜过我。","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"就算往饭里下毒，或者是在这城墙上推我一把，我也该死了千百遍了。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"我只怕你杀了我，也没法放下执念。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"......如果不是跟在你身边五年，听到这种话，我一定会大骂你是世上最道貌岸然的伪君子。","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"五年，竟然有这么久了。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#4$1","focus":"l","text":"","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"从你的视角看，未必是多长的一段时间吧。","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"这又怎么说？","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"十几年过去，一个人的相貌没有半点改变，脸上也总是挂着这副世事看尽的无奈表情，我再迟钝，也该明白你不是普通人。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"知道这片大地上有一些寿命极长的种族，以前只是当故事听，没想到就在自己的身边。","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"你早就想到了。","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/60/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"我只是不太在乎。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"我只为报仇，你能活多长和我没有关系。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"更何况，总想着你不是普通人，不就等于在为自己找借口。","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"就像你说的，徒步登高，只需要一步一步往上走就好了。其他的事情，想多了只是干扰心志。","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"但一心惦记着恩怨、输赢，就算真的得偿所愿，未必就能放下。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"剑上承载的杂念太多，就会变得迟缓。","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"普通人，总得靠那一点执念活着......你又何尝不清楚。","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"我记得刚认识的时候，你说话还没这么“咄咄逼人”......","id":105,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"这五年，我毕竟受了你不少教诲。","id":107,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"我教你的，只是习武的心得。","id":109,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"还是你说的，你能教的有限，但学到的比教的多，也是各人的造化。","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f3/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"......","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"话说回来，你总该去见见那些还记挂着你的人。","id":115,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_787_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"仇白","text":"你是太多人的执念了。","id":117,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avg_npc_787_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_2024_chyue_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"重岳","text":"......","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/60/Avg_avg_2024_chyue_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":120},{"type":"dialog","id":121},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":122},{"type":"charslot","id":123},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_bg_35_g9_yumensuburb.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":124},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":125},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$escape_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_dia_escape_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":126,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":127},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$1","posfrom":"-150,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1","id":128},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$1","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"那个大块头不见了......","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":132},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.7","id":133},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":134},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","posfrom":"-300,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1","id":135},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":136},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"站住。","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"又是你......","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"既然姑娘不是那伙贼人的同伙，又为何要偷剑？医馆那人和你又是什么关系？","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"我不认识他们，我也不知道那人是谁。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"显然你不清楚自己卷进了多大的麻烦。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你没在移动城市生活过，对玉门一无所知。有人告诉了你这把剑的位置，利用你将它盗走。","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f3/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"但这会招惹来怎样的麻烦，你并不知道。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f3/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"告诉我，事情或许还有挽回的余地。","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"我说过了，没有谁指示，我只是为了报恩。","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"哪怕自己会丢掉性命？","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":156},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":157},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":158},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"......反正你别再跟着我了。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"不管真相如何，我不能坐视一个无关的人因此陷入险境。","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"我是在救你。","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"......","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"嘴上说得再好听也没用。你不是个好人。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"我奉命追查，你盗剑在先，即使有些隐情，也不该颠倒黑白。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"就看你下令把工坊的那些师傅都抓去军营，你就不值得相信。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"他们试图掩护山海众逃离铸剑坊。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"他们是去保护那里的！","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cb/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"在嫌疑没有洗清之前，一应人等都需严查。天灾当前，贼寇作乱，我要对玉门负责。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"在我的部族，只有年满十六岁、身体强壮的阿纳萨，族人才会为他打造专门的武器。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"得到武器的阿纳萨，就要永远保护老人小孩，和生病的同胞。","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"说是不能看着无关的人陷入险境，说是为了保护一座城市，就可以轻易将武器对准普通人。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/60/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"左乐职责在身......","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"师父说得对，你们这些人，因为有冠冕堂皇的理由可以说，就不觉得自己做错了。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":188},{"type":"charslot","id":189},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":190},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#11$1","duration":"1.5","id":191},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"我还特地放慢了速度，结果一回头发现人没有跟上来。","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"剑还在我手上，你俩反倒聊起来了？","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"先生，左乐与二位有些误会，希望你可以交出佩剑，物归原主。","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#9$1","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"我听你们吵了半天，大概明白了意思。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"此剑原来是那位宗师的东西，但是被这位小姑娘给偷偷带走了。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"他的武功出神入化，肯定不依赖哪一件具体的兵器。难道还能是他舍不得这把剑，派你来追的？","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_297_1#2$1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"其中隐秘，不方便告知。","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c7/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#9$1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"要是给他添了麻烦，那他卸任的日子又得往后拖......但我也答应过要帮这个小姑娘。","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#3$1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"嗯......难办，难办。","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_297_1#9$1","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":208,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f3/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#9$1","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"有了。","id":210,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"大道理我懒得管，我倒有个直截了当的办法。","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"你们俩都算有点功夫，不如就在这儿打一架。都不许用武器，比拳头，谁赢了，我就把剑给谁。","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":213},{"type":"charslot","id":214},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","id":215},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"荒唐。苍生大事，岂能儿戏。","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"我是不会动手的——","id":218},{"type":"dialog","id":219},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1","posfrom":"200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"0.4","id":220},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":221},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_297_1#4$1","id":222},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.5","id":223},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":224},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"0.3","id":225},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":226},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"n","id":227},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"......我赶时间。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":230},{"type":"dialog","id":231},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":233},{"type":"charslot","id":234},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_bg_25_g04_yaninn.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":235},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":236},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_calm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":237,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":238},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch","volume":"0.8","id":239},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":240},{"type":"playsound","key":"$punch_n1","id":241},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch02","volume":"0.8","delay":"0.2","id":242},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":243},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch","volume":"0.8","id":244},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch02","volume":"0.5","delay":"0.2","id":245},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.5","delay":"0.6","id":246},{"type":"text","text":"梅花五点，拳脚相通；来留去送，甩手直冲。","id":247},{"type":"text","text":"寸内发劲，力有对错；意投于外，一点精神......","id":248},{"type":"dialog","id":249},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":251},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":252},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":253},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":254},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"哦？","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","id":257},{"type":"text","text":"天蒙蒙亮，客栈里的伙计才开始擦桌扫地，准备今日伙房要用的食材。","id":258},{"type":"text","text":"老鲤刚起床，后院已经传来羽兽晨鸣，以及，阵阵拳风。","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#2$1","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"终究是父女，缘分哪......","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":262},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":263},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"漂亮，漂亮。","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":266},{"type":"charslot","id":267},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":268},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"鲤叔......","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":271},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":272},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"有段时间没见过你打这套拳了，还以为你是忽然参透了什么心法，到了无招胜有招的境界。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"鲤叔又说玩笑话。","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"武功可不是这么玄乎的东西，想要进步，只有靠日复一日的苦练。","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"说得有理。","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"还记得第一次让你帮事务所跑腿，就招惹到了一群不太规矩的帮派。","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"等我反应过来赶到的时候，只看到你站在倒了一地的黑帮打手中间，像个没事人一样。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"那时候你才十六岁......","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"我在还没有太学会说话的时候，就已经开始习武了。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"那么早的事也能记得？","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"是他告诉我的......","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"至少在这方面，他把你教得很好。","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"老话都说，“师父领进门，修行看个人”。","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"好吧，其实“领进门”也是很重要的......","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"可能在他看来，这是作为父亲，唯一能为你做的事了。","id":297,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"......","id":299,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"我可没有替他开脱的意思。他不是个称职的父亲，但这不该妨碍你过一个自己想要的人生。","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"这身武功，你可以当作他送给你的礼物。要是不喜欢，就当是被报了一个不喜欢的兴趣班，扔下就是。","id":302,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"追求武学巅峰是他的道，但不一定是你的。","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"我不讨厌这身武功，我当然也有自己的人生。","id":305,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"我是龙门科技大学机械工程专业的优秀毕业生，是鲤氏侦探事务所的雇员，也是罗德岛的外勤干员。","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"但不是冬青木区大学生行侠仗义第一人。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"需要的话，我也可以是！","id":311,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dd/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"既然都想通了，下回见面的时候，把这些话告诉他就好。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"鲤叔，你果然......","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"突然打一套好久不练的拳，总归是有原因的。","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"话说回来，考虑到他这些年不负责任的行为，你要是不服气，确实可以去找他打一架。","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"输了也没关系，他在你这个年纪，也未必就比你厉害。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_322_lmlee_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_243_waaifu_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐琥","text":"......","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_243_waaifu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":323},{"type":"dialog","id":324},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"charslot","id":326},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_bg_35_g9_yumensuburb.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":327},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":328},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":329,"musicid":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":330},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.5","id":331},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"50","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":332},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":333},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch","id":334},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"40","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":335},{"type":"playsound","key":"$fightgeneral","volume":"0.5","delay":"0.4","id":336},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":337},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch","id":338},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":339},{"type":"playsound","key":"$punch_n1","delay":"0.3","id":340},{"type":"subtitle","text":"左乐作为秉烛人还很年轻，但处理过的大小事务，已经不能算少。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":341},{"type":"subtitle","text":"但其中没有哪件事逼得他不能出手，他学过的武功，也没有教他该怎样只挨打而不还击。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":342},{"type":"subtitle","text":"理亏吗？还是不愿欺负一个受伤的少女？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":343},{"type":"subtitle","text":"雨点般的拳头落在左乐身上，左乐只是招架。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":344},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","volume":"0.4","id":345},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","delay":"0.1","volume":"0.6","channel":"a","id":346},{"type":"subtitle","text":"两人双双摔倒在地，都是灰头土脸，少女还是不依不饶，挥拳越发拼命。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":347},{"type":"subtitle","text":"场面滑稽得像是顽童打架。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":348},{"type":"subtitle","id":349},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":350},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#3$1","duration":"0.5","id":351},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"（摇头叹气）","id":353,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#8$1","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"停。","id":355,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#1$1","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"我看得清楚，胜负已分，是这个小姑娘赢了。","id":357,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":358},{"type":"charslot","id":359},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":360},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":362},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#1$1","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"接着。","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":365},{"type":"charslot","id":366},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_scabbard","volume":"0.7","id":367},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$1","id":368},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"jump","posto":"0,0","power":"-10","times":"1","duration":"0.7","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":370},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#11$1","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"我姑且放你走，等你报完恩，再回来还医药费。","id":372,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"截云","text":"......好。","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_avg_4078_bdhkgt_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":375},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":376},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","id":377},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"350,0","duration":"1","id":378},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":379},{"type":"charslot","id":380},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#1$1","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"小子，你的刀也还给你。","id":382,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":383},{"type":"playsound","key":"$swordtsing1","volume":"0.7","id":384},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":385},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#9$1","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"看出来人家有伤，不还手，输倒也输得体面。","id":387,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":389,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_297_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_785_1#9$1","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"你也没必要用这种眼神看我。","id":391,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"小姑娘答应了我要回来，我信她。她要是言而无信，就是我看错人了。","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"槐天裴","text":"我帮你抓她回来。","id":393,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_785_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":394},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":395},{"type":"charslot","id":396},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_bg_35_g8_yumenarena.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":397},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#1$1","id":398},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_296_1#1$1","id":399},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_dooropen","volume":"0.6","id":400},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"可以走了。","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":403},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":404},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":405},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":406},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"......为什么这么看着我？","id":408,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"你看起来，没有受伤。","id":410,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"是意料之外还是失望？","id":412,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"我不希望你出事。","id":414,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"闹了一些不必要的误会，让你陷入麻烦了，抱歉。","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"刚才我已经和他们解释过了，没事了。","id":416,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"慢着。","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fd/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"刚才这里的军士告诉我，我手里的那只袖标——你给我的那一只，本来是前天从城外带回来的证物。","id":420,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"你不打算解释一下？","id":421,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"既然你已经知道了，又何必要我来解释。","id":423,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":424},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"all","id":425},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#5$1","id":426},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_singleblunt","id":427},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"5","randomness":"10","block":"false","id":428},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":429},{"type":"text","text":"杜遥夜的拳头停在了半空中，林雨霞也没有躲闪的意思。","id":430},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"我们才认识不久，你不相信我也在情理之中。","id":432,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"你想要找一个人帮你去查铸剑坊，我可以同意。","id":433,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"但你不该用我朋友的事来骗我。","id":434,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"对不......","id":436,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"停，打住。","id":438,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"你没资格跟我道歉，我不会原谅你。","id":439,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"好。","id":441,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":442},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"这就是你们龙门人的做事方式？","id":443,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"这是我自己的做事方式。","id":445,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"......","id":447,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"所以呢，总不能白白让你利用这一趟，你查到什么有用的东西了？","id":448,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"把你知道的事都告诉我。","id":449,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"原本只是一些怀疑，现在更加确信了。","id":451,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"从城外发现信使队伍遇袭开始，我们遇到的每件事都充满蹊跷。","id":453,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"你们在铸剑坊遇到山海众也并非巧合，这是那位姓孟的刀匠和他们有所勾结的最直接证据。","id":455,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"真的是他......？","id":457,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"如果有一人，有能力，也有理由一手策划这些事，那只能是他。","id":459,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"我不明白，他为什么要做这些事......","id":461,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_296_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":462},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杜遥夜","text":"我朋友的下落，你到底还知道多少？！","id":463,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_296_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"我不清楚，但已经派人去查了。","id":465,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#13$1","focus":"l","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"如果按最坏的打算来看，不单单是信使队伍，整座玉门城恐怕都已深陷极大的危险中。","id":467,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4080_lin_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"林雨霞","text":"但愿他的目的不在于此，或者是，还有后手......","id":469,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4080_lin_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":470},{"type":"dialog","id":471},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":472},{"type":"charslot","id":473},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_bg_35_g1_yumenstreet_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":474},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":475},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":476,"musicid":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":477},{"type":"subtitle","text":"几十年了，孟铁衣极少站在门外打量自己这间作坊。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":478},{"type":"subtitle","text":"待在里面时总觉得院子局促，从街上看，墙高砖厚，大门方正，倒还算气派。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":479},{"type":"subtitle","text":"为期一月的集市已经到了最后几天，街上依旧熙熙攘攘，门庭冷落的铸剑坊反而因此显眼起来。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":480},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“暂停营业”的牌子掉落在地上，取而代之的是两道白底红印的封条。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":481},{"type":"subtitle","text":"黑漆木门上的黄铜铆钉不知何时掉了一个，自己竟然一直没有发现，也没有人提醒自己。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":482},{"type":"subtitle","id":483},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":484},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":485},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_789_1#6$1","duration":"1.5","id":486},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":487},{"type":"dialogue","name":"孟铁衣","text":"唉......","id":488,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_789_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_789_1#4$1","id":489},{"type":"dialogue","name":"孟铁衣","text":"到底是老了，不中用了。最后一件事，也办不利索......","id":490,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_789_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":491},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":492},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":493},{"type":"image","id":494},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":495},{"type":"character","id":496},{"type":"image","id":497}],"characters":["重岳","仇白","截云","左乐","槐天裴","老鲤","槐琥","林雨霞","杜遥夜","孟铁衣"]}